body:
Features (all optional):

Increases glove size in 1st person to better match it's size when rendered in 3rd person;
Fixes vanilla capes (e.g. Migrator's cape) being rendered on top of Aether capes by hiding the vanilla cape;
Fixes Quark's emote system causing your arm to be rendered offset to your glove by disabling the system's rendering entirely. (disabled by default)

![comparison of how the glove is rendered in first person when just The Aether mod, with the Quark mod, and with this mod, showcasing the fixes described in the description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0c3dc858a582f83227a3a181648f9199f836ffcc.png)

![shows a comparison between how the valkyrie cape is rendered in third person with just The Aether mod and with this mod which applies the fixes mentioned in the description](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4503e172d314bc6a04b743c15fd7baf60069650c.png)
